init_text: A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She's unaware that she's actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who's fallen for her, and is certain he's going to get it right this time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: lives with a psychic parrot named Toots.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Toots decides he's going to help Lilybelle end this crazy dating cycle.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Toots uses his psychic powers to read the stars, thereby predicting Lilybelle's romantic future.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Toots, however is really bad at this.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He's also really bad at math, so his predictions are always off.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He can't seem to figure out how to get Lilybelle the right man at the right time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He can't seem to put her in a room with a man who will fit her life parameters.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He can't seem to get her out of a relationship when he knows it isn't right.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The only thing Toots is good at is getting Lilybelle into trouble.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You're going to find the perfect man for you today."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Toots takes off and Lilybelle heads to work.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: On her way, she stops in a store to buy some groceries.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She meets a man in the bakery section of the store.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They strike up a conversation and he offers to carry her groceries to her car.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He's perfect on paper; he's handsome, he has a great job, and he seems to really like her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He also seems to be exactly what she wants in a man.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He even offers to take her out on their first date that night.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Lilybelle rushes home to prepare herself for her date.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She starts to get dressed, but without looking closely at her clothes, something catches her eye.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She looks down and sees a large stain on her blouse.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "There's no way I'm going out with this guy looking like this, she says to herself."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "He's at the Olive Garden," she replies, "waiting for me.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Olive Garden is his favorite restaurant.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: can tell he really likes Lilybelle.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: happy for Lilybelle and goes off to play hide and seek with some neighborhood kids.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: relax and enjoy each other's company.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They get back to her place and start getting cozy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Let's get on the couch," says Lilybelle.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She pulls him onto the couch and they start getting really close.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She inches her hand onto his thigh and feels something she's never felt before.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Her hand feels a bulge emerge from behind his zipper.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She pulls back and looks at him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: His face is flushed and he looks nervous.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Lilybelle feels her hands grow hot.
